T01TD1137E:83b-1: na rag auddha ri n'a ma /
T01TD1137E:83b-3: dmyal ba nas 'don pa zhes bya ba /
T01TD1137E:83b-4: 'jig rten mgon po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1137E:83b-5: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho chen por ni //
T01TD1137E:83b-6: dbul ba'i 'dam du bying ba la //
T01TD1137E:83b-7: yongs su mkhyen pa bskyed nas ni //
T01TD1137E:83b-8: de bzhin gshegs kye bdag la skyobs //
T01TD1137E:83b-9: bdag ni rab rib khang par zhugs //
T01TD1137E:83b-10: mgon med sdug bsngal nyams su myong //
T01TD1137E:83b-11: bdag ni gnyen gyi tshogs kyis spangs //
T01TD1137E:83b-12: de bzhin gshegs kye bdag la skyobs //
T01TD1137E:83b-13: pha dang ma dang sring mo dang //
T01TD1137E:83b-14: bu dang chung ma mdza' bshes mo //
T01TD1137E:83b-16: de bzhin gshegs kye bdag la skyobs //
T01TD1137E:83b-18: las gang legs dang nyes byas pa //
T01TD1137E:84a-2: de bzhin gshegs kyi bdag la skyobs //
T01TD1137E:84a-3: khron rnying mi bzad chen po dang //
T01TD1137E:84a-4: gting med rgya mtsho dag rnams su //
T01TD1137E:84a-5: mgon po bdag cag long gyur na //
T01TD1137E:84a-6: de bzhin gshegs kye bdag la skyobs //
T01TD1137E:84a-7: rgya mtsho chen po rgal ba yi //
T01TD1137E:84a-8: gru ni gog por zhugs pa ltar //
T01TD1137E:84a-9: bdag gis kyang ni rgal dkar 'khums //
T01TD1137E:84a-10: de bzhin gshegs kye bdag la skyobs //
T01TD1137E:84a-11: chos dang chos min ma 'tshal zhing //
T01TD1137E:84a-12: bgrod dka' bgrod min mi rig pas //
T01TD1137E:84a-14: de bzhin gshegs kye bdag la skyobs //
T01TD1137E:84a-15: pha bsad pa dang ma bsad pa //
T01TD1137E:84a-16: kho bos mtshams med lnga bgyis pa //
T01TD1137E:84a-17: mi bzad rab rib mun par 'khums //
T01TD1137E:84a-18: de bzhin gshegs kye bdag la skyobs //
T01TD1137E:84a-19: bdag gis mchod rten 'jig par bgyis //
T01TD1137E:84a-21: bdag gis sems can 'tshe bar bgyis //
T01TD1137E:84a-22: de bzhin gshegs kye bdag la skyobs //
T01TD1137E:84a-25: las kyi srad bus dkris pas na //
T01TD1137E:84a-26: de bzhin gshegs kye bdag la skyobs //
T01TD1137E:84a-28: mkha' la ka shi'i me tog ni //
T01TD1137E:84a-29: rlung gis btab nas 'phyan pa bzhin //
T01TD1137E:84a-30: de bzhin gshegs kye bdag la skyobs //
T01TD1137E:84a-31: 'brog dgon dang ni tsher ma yi //
T01TD1137E:84a-32: ljon shing mang po rten med pa //
T01TD1137E:84a-33: de na bdag gis lam ma mthong //
T01TD1137E:84a-34: de bzhin gshegs kye bdag la skyobs //
T01TD1137E:84a-35: nyes pa med par phyugs rnams dang //
T01TD1137E:84a-36: ri dags mang po mdas bsad pas //
T01TD1137E:84a-37: de tshe bdag ni rgyal por rlom //
T01TD1137E:84a-38: de bzhin gshegs kye bdag la skyobs //
T01TD1137E:84a-39: sems can dmyal bar 'tshed pa na //
T01TD1137E:84a-40: skyob pa 'ga' yang yod ma mchis //
T01TD1137E:84a-41: gang la skyabs su mchi bar bgyi //
T01TD1137E:84a-42: bdag la skyob par su zhig 'gyur //
T01TD1137E:84a-43: sman pa rnams kyi sman pa'i rgyal //
T01TD1137E:84a-44: nad rnams thams cad gso mdzad pa //
T01TD1137E:84a-45: khams gsum rgyu dang mi rgyu ba //
T01TD1137E:84a-46: skyob byed 'jig rten mgon po lags //
T01TD1137E:84a-47: dmyal ba nas 'don pa zhes bya ba slob dpon chen po klu sgrub kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so//
